  }, "v4"), mdx("p", null, "Khi Gi\xEA-xa-b\xEAn gi\u1EBFt c\xE1c nh\xE0 ti\xEAn tri c\u1EE7a CH\xDAA th\xEC \xC1p-\u0111ia gi\u1EA5u m\u1ED9t tr\u0103m ti\xEAn tri trong hai hang \u0111\xE1, m\u1ED7i hang n\u0103m m\u01B0\u01A1i ng\u01B0\u1EDDi. \xD4ng mang th\u1EE9c \u0103n v\xE0 n\u01B0\u1EDBc u\u1ED1ng cho h\u1ECD. "), mdx("h6", {
