    "id": "v7"
  }, "v7"), mdx("p", null, "Trong khi \xC1p-\u0111ia \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng th\xEC \xCA-li g\u1EB7p \xF4ng. \xC1p-\u0111ia nh\u1EADn ra \xCA-li n\xEAn c\xFAi r\u1EA1p xu\u1ED1ng \u0111\u1EA5t v\xE0 th\u01B0a, \"Th\u1EA7y c\xF3 ph\u1EA3i l\xE0 \xCA-li kh\xF4ng?\" "), mdx("h6", {
