  }, "v12"), mdx("p", null, "R\u1ED3i l\u1EE1 Th\u1EA7n Linh c\u1EE7a CH\xDAA mang \xF4ng \u0111i n\u01A1i kh\xE1c sau khi t\xF4i r\u1EDDi \xF4ng th\xEC sao? N\u1EBFu t\xF4i \u0111i b\u1EA3o A-h\xE1p r\u1EB1ng \xF4ng \u1EDF \u0111\xE2y m\xE0 vua \u0111\u1EBFn kh\xF4ng g\u1EB7p \xF4ng th\xEC m\u1EA1ng t\xF4i s\u1EBD kh\xF4ng c\xF2n! T\xF4i \u0111\xE3 theo CH\xDAA t\u1EEB khi c\xF2n nh\u1ECF. "), mdx("h6", {
